Generate License                   Template Settings
  â†“                                  â†“
Send to: customer@example.com   â†’  To Email: {{to_email}}
  â†“                                  â†“
EmailJS receives:                  EmailJS sends email to:
to_email = "customer@example.com"  customer@example.com âœ…
```

---

## âš ï¸ COMMON MISTAKES:

### Mistake 1: Single Curly Braces
```
To Email: {to_email}         âŒ WRONG (single braces)
To Email: {{to_email}}       âœ… CORRECT (double braces)
```

### Mistake 2: Wrong Variable Name
```
To Email: {{email}}          âŒ WRONG (doesn't match)
To Email: {{to_email}}       âœ… CORRECT (matches what we send)
```

### Mistake 3: Extra Spaces
```
To Email: {{ to_email }}     âŒ WRONG (spaces inside)
To Email: {{to_email}}       âœ… CORRECT (no spaces)
```

### Mistake 4: Capital Letters
```
To Email: {{To_Email}}       âŒ WRONG (capitals)
To Email: {{to_email}}       âœ… CORRECT (lowercase)
```

